show.description: After sacrificing everything to fund her son Damien’s education, Catherine moves to the city to reunite with his growing family. But Damien disowns her, posing as her nephew, and his wife Ravenna falsely accuses her of theft. Forced into servitude as a nanny, Catherine faces betrayal where she expected love.
